
Quick A/N: I'm really excited to be working on a new story.. I really hope you like how it turns out!!
Louis Tomlinson world renown owner of LoTom Record Co. He doesn't always have everything he wants, but with some elbow grease he can get it.
Harry Styles a simple baker with a dream of becoming a famous singer. He always strived to get higher up in the social status, to have people recognize him.
One day, Louis finds his way into the bakery that Harry works at. Liking the food, he comes back again and again until he becomes a regular. Will Styles fall for his diamond-like eyes? Will Tomlinson push him away because he trusts only a few people with his life?